# ===================================

# Infura: 100,000 requests/day, 10 requests/second
# Alchemy: 300M compute units/month
# Moralis: 100M compute units/month
# CoinGecko: 50 calls/minute (with free API key)
# BlockCypher: 200 requests/hour, 3 requests/second
